haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Ltn Patrik Schorner, Ltn Patrik Schorner

 The mission was flown from Pukov aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 05/04/1916 near Factory.
A F.E.2b of 3rd KAO was brought down by Siegfried Ganzfried of FA 15.
SPk Jeirgif Polsky was killed in action.
Pk Yurii Kortnev was killed in action.
Siegfried Ganzfried was  flying a Roland C.IIa.
